data.title: Britannia Industries: Indian Kolkata Wadia Group Nusli Wadia
data.meta_description: Britannia Industries - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Britannia Industries is an Indian food products corporation founded in 1892 and headquartered in Kolkata. It is one of India's oldest existing companies and is now part of the Wadia Group. The company sells its popular Britannia and Tiger brands of biscuits, breads, and dairy products throughout India and in over 60 countries worldwide. Britannia enjoys a large market share in India and is very profitable. However, it has faced some controversies related to its management in recent decades.
